  <p>The bad – Discovering that you can’t scaffold something which has 2 relationships.</p>

  <p>The bodge – Restarting the app from scratch 4 times instead of fixing the problems.</p>

    <p><strong>Learnings:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Don’t name your app the same thing as you want to name one of your controllers</li>
        <li>You can’t scaffold something that has 2 relationships</li>
      </ul>
